    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been a fantastic ride for me and is still in really solid, reliable shape. It handles beautifully and is just waiting for someone to take it on its next big adventure. If you're looking for a dependable set of wheels that\u2019s been well-cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
