    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained SUV offers the perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior shines with a deep luster, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any tears or stains, and the cabin still carries that clean, well-cared-for aroma. Mechanically, this vehicle is sound; it has a documented service history including a recent oil change, brake pad replacement, and a fresh set of all-season tires with significant tread remaining. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the touchscreen navigation, functions exactly as it should. This is a dependable, honest vehicle that has many miles of comfortable service left to offer its next owner.",
      "price": 31850.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
